{
  "stem": "9538.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where with-- they had already those uniforms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The striped uniforms.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And had different triangles on their jackets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Green ones were for the [GERMAN] [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] for the worst criminals.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And mauve were for homosexuals.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Pink was for [GERMAN], Jehovah's Witnesses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So but they were not so bad, but the ones with the green-- green triangles, they were the ones who were murderers and-- and the greatest crooks.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were in charge of the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Directly in charge.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were the kapos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kapo is camp police.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Kapo is an abbreviation for camp police, but camp written with a K.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so my father was tortured.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was kicked so much so that he-- for-- until the rest of his life, he walked with a limp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They hit a nerve, and the muscles sort of-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Withered.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he walked with that to the end of his life, with a limp, because of that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he came back from Buchenwald in terrible pain, and he walked with a limp until the rest of this life.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, then-- from then on, it went from bad to worse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He came back about Christmas of-- of '38.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just around about Christmastime.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He was there about a month, or six weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All over Germany, the Germans were not-- the Jews were not allowed to live near Germans or with Germans in the same house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they erected Jewish houses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They called it Judenhause.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had to leave our big house and had to go into a very small Jewish house with four families.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were-- lived there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
